---
title: One-Pan Chorizo Risoni Risotto with Cherry Tomatoes, Silverbeet & Cheddar
description: We believe weeknight dinners should be tasty and on the table without too much fuss. Hence, we present you with our risoni risotto. Minimal stirring, loads of comforting ooziness and superbly satisfying… what could be better?
